There was a problem with the previous version as the cell are reusable and checkmark attribute is releted to cell so it checks when it is reused
To solve the above problem we converted the approach to mvc architecture
However to store the data using user defaults, we needed consistent data type so we switched to custom plist mode of storing the data to store it in format of our model class Item type
This module covers the creation of custom plist and use of encodable and decodable classes to store the data in plist
